00:09:51,591 --> 00:09:52,926
Matikan kameranya.

75
00:09:53,426 --> 00:09:55,929
Brock, para mitra ingin tahu
bagaimana perkembangannya.

76
00:09:57,514 --> 00:10:00,725
Hai, Dave. Hai, Barry.
Ternyata tak ada di dalam peti.

77
00:10:00,809 --> 00:10:02,310
Namun, jangan khawatirkan itu.

78
00:10:02,393 --> 00:10:05,522
Masih ada banyak
kemungkinan tempat lain. Pasti.

79
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:07,774
Reruntuhan lantai
di suite, kamar ibu,

80
